this was forked from https://github.com/lydell/VimFx-config/

1. about:config

2. set xpinstall.{signatures,whitelist}.required to false

3. ln -s <path-to-VimFx-config@vimfx.org> ~/.mozilla/firefox/<profile>/extensions/

4. ln -s <path-to-userChrome.css> ~/.mozilla/firefox/<profile>/chrome/

5. restart firefox. check cmd line errors or browser console